    "en": "Apply to PFA-fixed cells only. Incubate at RT for 10–15 min. Triton concentration can range 0.1–0.5%; higher concentrations increase permeabilization but reduce morphology preservation. Use 0.5% for nuclear antigens. Wash 3× with PBS before immunostaining.",
    "zh": "用于固定后的细胞透化 (PFA 固定后)。室温处理 10–15 min。Triton 浓度 0.1–0.5% 可选，浓度越高透化越强但形态保存越差。对于核抗原，0.5% 效果更好。使用后 PBS 洗 3 次再做免疫染色。"
  },
